{"title":"我是山的儿子","authors":["赵晓春"],"dates":[{"year":1986,"month":1,"day":13}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"我是山的儿子"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"赵晓春"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我是山的儿子，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"拥有山的一切。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"弯曲的小径，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是我缠绵的思绪；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"高高的山脊，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是我沉重的记忆；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"阳光下的阵阵林涛，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是我心潮的起伏；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"月光下的声声叶音，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是我梦中的低语。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"更有那遍山的小草，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是我心中的一块碧玉……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有一天，我做了一个梦"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小草悄悄对我说："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“当我爬上你的肩胛，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你在我眼里就是一座山。”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"呵！我真高兴，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我高兴我是山的儿子，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我相信我不会死去。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}